public class ProduceOrdersController.TableRow extends Object
This class is a TableRow for Sales table in this page all these variables are defining details of our stock transactions the class has a constructor that allows us to set the data through it, we also have getters and setters for each variables as well we use this class mainly to add each instance into a row of the table we have
